data.description: Known as the Gray Lady,  you will love this charming and well-maintained 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with an optional 6th bedroom/den located in Elkridge. It boasts several attractive features, including: Hardwood Floors,  which are not only durable but also add a touch of elegance to the interior, Stainless Steel Appliances in the large country-style kitchen, Updated Bathrooms, which enhances comfort and aesthetics, a large Maintenance-Free Front Porch, a Fenced Backyard, which provides privacy and the ideal space for outdoor activities and relaxation, and a Loft-Style Primary Bedroom, which includes custom closets. The home has also seen various recent improvements, such as heated bathroom floors, new stove and dishwasher in 2023, a new sump pump in 2019, new shutters in 2022, new roof 2018, and a new fence in 2022. The property is conveniently located, offering easy access to various amenities and services, making it an attractive choice for potential buyers, and perfect for hosting and entertaining family and friends.  This is a lovely and well-maintained home with several appealing features for potential homeowners.
